<br>
Was hunting in Velk's yesterday morning killing spiders and statues for 3-4 hours.  If I recall some of the folks in the group there were Qelin, Unleashed, Maxiemus, Khandhara and others throughout the morning, who came and went.  If I forgot you I apologize, but probably for the best.  Well, Jimi joins the group and spiders/statues are going down with no problems.  Experience is flowing nicely, and all are happy.  At times the group had no healers which didn't seem to be a problem, because we were able to keep the adds mezzed and deal with them in turn.<br>
<br>
